{"tid":543903,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)吉列合唱團/基佬合唱團 第一季","createTime":"2018-01-29T03:56:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-01T09:40:59.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"67dbad0f264b68157eb16bd2f45b72df36a25b4d","tid":543903,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T03:56:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">播唔完下次播返</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=nKaxyJspJgObJ3cc5PIlbTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=509251e1\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=nKaxyJspJgObJ3cc5PIlbTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=c6ad1c78\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=nKaxyJspJgObJ3cc5PIlbTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=ab9607e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/glee/images/d/d7/Glee-glee-6211974-2560-1922.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20130408030726\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fglee%2Fimages%2Fd%2Fd7%2FGlee-glee-6211974-2560-1922.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20130408030726&h=47932ac5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMcKinley高中合唱團曾經過輝煌的過去，但隨著歲月的流逝，早已灰暗。教師Will（馬修&middot;莫里森Matthew Morrison飾）接受了艱鉅的任務：重塑合唱團形象。但擺在面前的 現實是：校啦啦隊教練Sue（簡&middot;林奇Jane Lynch飾）的萬般阻撓。來參加的學生五花八門。男高音Kurt（克里斯&middot;柯爾弗Chris Colfer飾）有表現力但愚笨;見習主唱不肯 唱背景和聲;吉他手總失踪。將把希望寄託在Rachel（麗亞&middot;米雪兒Lea Michele飾）和Finn（柯瑞&middot;蒙特斯Cory Monteith飾）身上。但他的女友Quinn（迪安娜&middot; 阿格隆Dianna Agron飾）和橄欖球隊隊友卻總給他惹麻煩。<br />\n請問能夠堅持自己的夢想和孩子們一起走下去嗎<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=nKaxyJspJgObJ3cc5PIlbTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=b5431ced\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=nKaxyJspJgObJ3cc5PIlbTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=037a6650\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d14a188152ed03d476d4f5b831ff1ede196a8fd0","tid":543903,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T03:57:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4826cd9f874ea7851803dbe4aebb80e895a051e","tid":543903,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T04:46:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"defe33489e16b7d3fea0472ff5f5b56d8a4c98ae","tid":543903,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T05:11:58.000Z","